Stormpath,is,a,cloud,based,service,that,is,used,to,manage,users,and,ease,authentication,and,access,control,within,applications,The,API,provides,programmatic,access,to,the,functionality,of,the,service,This,includes,basic,CRUD,operations,on,accounts,applications,directories,groups,and,tenants,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON,Full,documentation,is,not,publicly,available